summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the condemnation proceedings to acquire land and other property necessary for the laying off, opening, widening and establishing of Olson Place Southwest between Southwest Roxbury Street and First Avenue South (Secondary State Highway No. 1-K0, all as contemplated by Ordinance 99278, King County Cause No. 741002; accepting a condemnation award (Parcel 8) in connection therewith and making a reimbursable appropriation from the Arterial City Street Fund therefor.
